---
title: Easy Garlic & Herb Beef with Roast Veggie Toss & Peppercorn Aioli
description: A crispy stack of colourful roasted veggies creates the base for a steak dish of joyous proportions. Tender slices of beef rump are
adorned in herby seasoning and topped by peppercorn aioli to take things up a notch. Now, if that doesn't sound like heaven on
earth, we don't know what does!
